research/history/patches/round_0280.patch:17: | `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(x)} α_{s,i}^sh b_{s,i}^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}` | candidate | 两个 always-on shared 静态子库负责更厚的 coarse 主干，product-key router 只在静态 expert 子库间选择，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support；最终仍是静态库有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
research/history/patches/round_0280.patch:18:+| `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1(x))} α_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_2(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r_2(x))} α_{e,m} b_{e,m}` | candidate | 两个 shared 静态子库不是并行竞争同一 top-k，而是先后在 residual 上串联清理主干，再接 PK expert cleanup；仍只访问静态子库并做有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
research/history/patches/round_0280.patch:19: | `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(x)} α_{s,i}^sh b_{s,i}^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}` | candidate | 两个 always-on shared 静态子库负责 coarse 主干，PK router 按 token 难度自适应地启用 1 或 2 个静态 expert 子库，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support；最终仍是静态库有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
