research/history/round_summaries/round_0148.json:63:    "description": "建议以 r146 为 reference，仅设置 `ARCHITECTURE=two_stage_residual_expert`。这是一次低到中成本带的 matched architecture probe：在约 0.48x total_cost 下复验 trunk-free staged residual expert，直接判断“coarse library + expert residual”是否比当前已测的 shared-lowrank hetero residual 更值得继续。",
