research/history/logs/agent_action_0278.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(h(x))} α_{s,i}^{sh}(h(x)) b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是低秩 shared bottleneck，{b_{s,i}^{sh}} 是两个静态 shared coarse 子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_sΣ_i α_{s,i}^{sh}b_{s,i}^{sh}，{B_e} 是静态 PK-routed expert 子库，E_pk(·) 由 low-rank hidden 上的 left/right product-key 路由选出少量 experts，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + PK expert 选择 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r263 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，用极轻的 dual low-rank shared coarse branch 替代 plain PK 的无主干设置，同时保留 full-expert PK cleanup，能够在 exact `total_cost_ratio=0.082427978515625` 的近同成本档位比 r277 的 single-shared lowrank 变体显著更稳住 exceed，并争取在保持低成本的同时压低 exceed_alpha_0.50 到 `0.19357784271240236` 以下以击败 r263。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 `0.08243x` 下明显优于 r263，并接近或击败 r266，则下一轮应留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125`，测试更轻 shared split 是否能进一步提升 low-cost objective。","如果该 family 只比 r277 好、但仍明显输给 plain PK 或 incumbent，则记录为“dual low-rank shared coarse 修复了 single-shared lowrank 的容量不足，但 lowrank shared family 仍不够强”，后续不要继续在这条线做低信息细扫。","如果该 family 仍明显失败，则可更果断地下调“lowrank shared coarse + PK cleanup”整条方向优先级，把预算转向其他真正改变 cleanup 语义的新结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 与 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：low-rank shared coarse 子库从 1 个扩到 2 个；与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 分支改为 low-rank bottleneck 上的 factorized heads，而 routed cleanup 仍保留 full-expert PK JumpReLU encoders。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","实现中继续将实际 shared hidden 维度限制为 `min(FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT)`；在当前 recipe 下实际 hidden_dim=56，因此新增第二个 shared lowrank head 的成本很低。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=181888 (`0.043365478515625x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=345728 (`0.082427978515625x`)；这比 r277 的 single-shared lowrank 变体仅高 `0.0007476806640625x`，但 shared coarse 容量翻倍。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 16 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","r277 已给出强负信号：`shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在 `0.081680x` 下 exceed 达到 `0.223148`，说明 single-shared lowrank coarse 明显容量不足；本轮新 family 正是最小成本地测试这个结论是否能通过双 shared heads 被修复。"],"reference_round":263,"self_review":"这轮符合当前阶段优先级。r274-r277 已连续探索了 dual-shared、adaptive、single-shared-lowrank 三个不同槽位，其中只有 dual-shared 给出一定正向 exceed 信号，而最新 r277 证明“single lowrank shared coarse + PK cleanup”虽然极便宜，但 exceed 崩得太厉害。选择 `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的理由不是继续做邻域插值，而是用一个最小新结构直接回答 r277 暴露出的核心问题：失败是来自 lowrank shared 表达本身，还是来自 shared coarse 容量太薄。相对 r263 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，满足单变量规则；代码侧只新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke。主要风险是即便 shared coarse 翻倍，lowrank shared 表达仍可能不够，导致 exceed 仍远高于 target；但这轮会以很低的额外成本给出一个高信息量结论。","summary":"已新增并接通 `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r263 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚的 low-rank shared coarse + full-expert PK cleanup”能否在 `0.08243x` 的低成本档位修复 r277 的 exceed 崩塌。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0217.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_shared(h(x))} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(h(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(h(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `h(x)` \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf factorized scorer \u7684\u4e2d\u95f4\u8868\u793a\uff0c`{b_i^sh}` \u4e0e `{b_{e,j}}` \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u8f7b\u91cf\u9009\u62e9/\u8def\u7531 + shared \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + routed \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u4e5f\u4ecd\u662f\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u662f\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5f53\u524d incumbent r212 \u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u74f6\u9888\u5df2\u7ecf\u66f4\u504f\u5411 exceed \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7eaf cost\uff0c\u4f46\u6700\u8fd1\u51e0\u6761\u66f4\u91cd\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u5728 `0.19x~0.21x` cost \u5e26\u90fd\u6ca1\u6709\u62ff\u5230\u8db3\u591f\u7684 exceed \u56de\u62a5\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=128`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u66f4\u8f7b\u7684 factorized shared+routed scorer \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u663e\u8457\u66f4\u4f4e total_cost \u4e0b\uff0c\u628a exceed \u7ef4\u6301\u5728\u4ecd\u53ef\u8d62\u533a\u95f4\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=442368\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=606208\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.14453125\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684 exact 0.1640625 \u4e0b\u964d\u4e86 0.01953125\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ea\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u22640.21507` \u5c31\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d objective anchor\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u6bd4\u6700\u8fd1\u51e0\u6761 `0.21x` \u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u8981\u6c42\u7684 `\u22640.1487` \u660e\u663e\u73b0\u5b9e\uff0c\u4e14\u5b83\u6b63\u5bf9\u5e94\u5f53\u524d operator guide \u7684\u201c\u66f4\u8f7b scorer / router\u201d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u95ee\u9898\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0217.json:25:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u6211\u6ca1\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u6cbf `expert_topk` \u6216\u521a\u8dd1\u8fc7\u7684 `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u505a\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u5df2\u8fde\u7eed 4 \u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u6539\u8fdb\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u6700\u8fd1\u51e0\u6761 cost \u66f4\u9ad8\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u5df2\u7ecf\u7ed9\u51fa\u8f83\u6e05\u6670\u7684\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a\u5b83\u4eec\u80fd\u964d\u4e00\u70b9 exceed\uff0c\u4f46\u4ea4\u6362\u7387\u4e0d\u8db3\u4ee5\u652f\u6491 0.30 \u76ee\u6807\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` \u7684\u98ce\u9669\u5f88\u660e\u786e\uff1acurrent-target \u4e0a `factorized_expert_topk` \u5728 r211 \u7684 exceed=0.332294 \u5f88\u5dee\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e factorized selector \u53ef\u80fd\u660e\u663e\u4f24\u5bb3 support \u8d28\u91cf\uff1b\u65e7\u7684 r177 \u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u7ed9\u51fa shared+routed factorized \u7684\u6b63\u9762\u8bc1\u636e\u3002\u6240\u4ee5\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f\u4fdd\u5b88\u8d62\u9762\u6700\u9ad8\u7684\u4e00\u6b65\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u8f6e\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u88c1\u51b3\u3002\u5982\u679c\u5b83\u4ecd\u5728\u4f4e cost \u4e0b\u5b88\u4e0d\u4f4f exceed\uff0c\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u66f4\u679c\u65ad\u5730\u628a factorized-expert \u7ebf\u6574\u4f53\u964d\u7ea7\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u5b83\u80fd\u5728 `~0.145x` cost \u5e26\u628a exceed \u62c9\u56de `\u22640.215`\uff0c\u5219\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u4e0a\u771f\u6b63\u7f3a\u7684\u662f\u66f4\u8f7b\u7684\u9009\u62e9\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u66f4\u91cd\u7684 shared/coarse \u4e3b\u5e72\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0217.json:35:      "\u5f53\u524d incumbent r212 = objective 0.359600\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d cost 0.1640625\u3001exceed 0.195538\uff1b\u76f8\u8f83\u4e4b\u4e0b\uff0c\u6700\u8fd1 `lowrank_expert_topk` / `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` / `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u4e09\u6761\u66f4\u91cd\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u90fd\u4e3b\u8981\u5361\u5728 cost \u4e0a\u5347\u5feb\u4e8e exceed \u4e0b\u964d\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0217.json:73:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u6211\u6ca1\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u6cbf `expert_topk` \u6216\u521a\u8dd1\u8fc7\u7684 `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u505a\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u5df2\u8fde\u7eed 4 \u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u6539\u8fdb\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u6700\u8fd1\u51e0\u6761 cost \u66f4\u9ad8\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u5df2\u7ecf\u7ed9\u51fa\u8f83\u6e05\u6670\u7684\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a\u5b83\u4eec\u80fd\u964d\u4e00\u70b9 exceed\uff0c\u4f46\u4ea4\u6362\u7387\u4e0d\u8db3\u4ee5\u652f\u6491 0.30 \u76ee\u6807\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` \u7684\u98ce\u9669\u5f88\u660e\u786e\uff1acurrent-target \u4e0a `factorized_expert_topk` \u5728 r211 \u7684 exceed=0.332294 \u5f88\u5dee\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e factorized selector \u53ef\u80fd\u660e\u663e\u4f24\u5bb3 support \u8d28\u91cf\uff1b\u65e7\u7684 r177 \u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u7ed9\u51fa shared+routed factorized \u7684\u6b63\u9762\u8bc1\u636e\u3002\u6240\u4ee5\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f\u4fdd\u5b88\u8d62\u9762\u6700\u9ad8\u7684\u4e00\u6b65\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u8f6e\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u88c1\u51b3\u3002\u5982\u679c\u5b83\u4ecd\u5728\u4f4e cost \u4e0b\u5b88\u4e0d\u4f4f exceed\uff0c\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u66f4\u679c\u65ad\u5730\u628a factorized-expert \u7ebf\u6574\u4f53\u964d\u7ea7\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u5b83\u80fd\u5728 `~0.145x` cost \u5e26\u628a exceed \u62c9\u56de `\u22640.215`\uff0c\u5219\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u4e0a\u771f\u6b63\u7f3a\u7684\u662f\u66f4\u8f7b\u7684\u9009\u62e9\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u66f4\u91cd\u7684 shared/coarse \u4e3b\u5e72\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0233.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_router_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"factorized_router_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(R_down x) 仅用于轻量 router 选出少量 active experts，{b_{e,i}} 仍是各 expert 的静态子库原子，而 expert 内部系数 α_{e,i}(x) 仍由 full-dim local head 直接从输入 x 计算。在线导出链路仍是“低秩 router 投影 -> 选择少量静态 expert 子库 -> 子库内 local top-k -> 查表加权求和 -> 选择性补偿”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 可判为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能进入当前兼容 leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：当前 `expert_topk@K=32` 的主优势来自短 active path，而不是 full-dim router 本身；因此相对 r212 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到新实现的 `factorized_router_expert_topk`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 与其余主 recipe 不变，直接测试“只压轻 router、保留 full expert heads”能否在几乎不伤 exceed 的前提下进一步降低 objective。该实现将 router hidden 宽度限制为 `min(FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM, NUM_EXPERTS//2)`；在当前 matched recipe 下实际为 64，因此本地 exact 成本复核得到 selection_accesses=466944、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=630784，对 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy 的 exact total_cost_ratio=0.150390625。相对 r212 的 exact 0.1640625 释放出约 0.013672 的 objective 空间，因此只要 exceed_alpha_0.50 保持在约 `≤0.205147`，这轮就有现实机会刷新当前 incumbent。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_router_expert_topk@K32` 刷新 r212，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=48`，确认 router 是否还能继续压缩而不显著抬高 exceed。","如果该点 objective 接近但仍略输给 r212，且主要败在 exceed 而不是 cost，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=48`，测试是否应把省下的 router 成本部分回投到 lookup budget。","如果该点复现明显 exceed 回退，则说明当前 small-K lane 的关键并不只是 router 过重；后续应停止在“router-only 低秩化”这条线继续消耗预算，转回别的结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `factorized_router_expert_topk`，修改仅在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`；没有新增 tunable env key，也没有改执行层接线。","`factorized_router_expert_topk` 的结构语义是“低秩 router + full expert heads”：router 使用 `router_down -> router` 两层低秩路径，expert 内部 local head 仍保持 full-dim，因此它不是已被否定的 `factorized_expert_topk` 复刻。","本地 smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='factorized_router_expert_topk', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=128, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=192, factorized_hidden_dim=256)` 在 CPU 上可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地成本复核：`factorized_router_expert_topk K=32 NUM_EXPERTS=128 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 selection_accesses=466944、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=630784、exact total_cost_ratio=0.150390625。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key: ARCHITECTURE, value: factorized_router_expert_topk}], fallback_architecture='expert_topk')` 返回空列表。"],"reference_round":212,"self_review":"这轮满足当前 round-233 的 matched architecture probe 约束：相对 r212 的完整配置，只改变 `ARCHITECTURE`；`K`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR`、`OPTIMIZER`、`LR` 与其余主 recipe 都保持不变。之所以不继续从现有已注册 family 中挑 probe，是因为当前 `K=32` matched lane 上的 `lowrank_expert_topk`、`shared_routed_expert_topk`、`shared_two_stage_residual_expert`、`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`、`factorized_topk`、`factorized_expert_topk` 等主要结构槽位都已给出明确负信号，而剩余未闭合 family 的 exact cost 大多已远离 `0.18x~0.22x` 主战场。新 family 的工程改动被控制在 `sparsify/`，没有引入新参数接线风险；同时它正对当前高优先级的“更轻 scorer / router”问题，但比 `factorized_expert_topk` 更保守，因为只低秩化 router、保留 full expert heads。主要风险是 router 压缩仍可能破坏 expert 选择质量；但如果连这种最小侵入的 router-only 低秩化都守不住 exceed，就可以更果断地下调这条方向的优先级。","summary":"已新增并本地验证 `factorized_router_expert_topk`。建议以 r212 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_router_expert_topk`，做一轮新的 matched architecture probe，直接回答“router-only 低秩化”能否在保持 short active path 优势的同时，把 objective 从当前 0.3555 再往下推。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0207.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0207.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{j\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r\uff1b{u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{b_{e,j}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002r205-r206 \u5df2\u628a `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5728 `K=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` \u8fd9\u6761 lane \u7684 coarse/cleanup \u5206\u5de5\u57fa\u672c\u6478\u6e05\uff1a`STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` \u867d\u628a objective \u4ece 0.398672 \u538b\u5230 0.396941\uff0c\u4f46\u4ecd\u672a\u8d8a\u8fc7 r159 \u7684 0.395234\uff0c\u66f4\u6ca1\u6709\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent 0.386114\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u8fd9\u6761 family \u4e0a\u505a budget split \u7ec6\u626b\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\u4ef7\u503c\u5df2\u7ecf\u660e\u663e\u4e0b\u964d\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r201 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cshared coarse + routed residual cleanup\u201d\u76f8\u6bd4\u201clow-rank trunk + expert head\u201d\u5230\u5e95\u662f\u4e0d\u662f\u5f53\u524d 0.20x \u5de6\u53f3 lane \u7684\u6b63\u786e\u5bb9\u91cf\u5206\u5de5\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\uff0c\u8be5\u5019\u9009\u7684 combined_accesses=835584\u3001actual total_cost_ratio\u22480.199219x\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e r201/r206 \u7684 0.210938x\uff1b\u5982\u679c exceed \u4ecd\u80fd\u7ef4\u6301\u5728\u8be5 family \u5df2\u77e5\u7684\u7ea6 0.188 \u9644\u8fd1\uff0c\u5219 objective \u5c06\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u538b\u5230 0.39 \u9644\u8fd1\u5e76\u6311\u6218\u5f53\u524d\u6b21\u4f18\u517c\u5bb9\u70b9\u3002",
