research/history/logs/agent_action_0273.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式：x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e^τ(r(x))} α_{e,i}(r(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 r(x)=x-Σ_r β_r(x)u_r；U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，E_pk(·) 由 left/right product-key 路由选出少量 expert，expert 内再用 JumpReLU 形成局部 support。它可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“trunk 查表 + residual 上的 PK expert 选择 + expert 子库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此判定为扩展兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r266 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到 `lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，用 dense low-rank trunk 替代 always-on sparse shared stage，同时保留 PK tiny cleanup，能在 exact `total_cost_ratio=0.109375` 下把 exceed_alpha_0.50 压到 `0.165626` 以下，从而击败 r266。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["若该 family 在约 `0.109375x` cost 下明显压低 exceed 并赢过 r266，下一轮只改 `TRUNK_RANK=24`，测试更强 trunk 是否继续改善 objective。","若 exceed 仅小幅下降且 objective 仍不如 r266，则记录为“low-rank trunk + PK cleanup` 不足以替代 shared sparse coarse”，停止继续给这条线追加预算。","若该 probe 明显失败，则下调 `lowrank trunk + PK cleanup` 优先级，转向其他直接针对 small-K exceed 的新结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新 family `lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，包含 whitelist、factory dispatch、实现类与 override allowlist 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, trunk_rank=16, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地成本复核：selection_accesses=212992 (`0.05078125x`)，deployment_accesses=245760 (`0.05859375x`)，combined_accesses=458752 (`0.109375x`)；相对 r266 的 objective 门槛对应 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.165626`。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `extended_compatible`。"],"reference_round":266,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：运行配置相对 r266 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。代码侧新增 family 已完成最小必要接线，并补了 compatibility registry 记录；没有引入新 tunable key，因此不需要改 `config_resolution`、`runner` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是 dense trunk 带来的额外 deploy cost（相对 r266 多 `0.013671875x`）换不回足够的 exceed 改善；但这正是一个高信息量的 matched architecture probe，能直接回答“shared sparse coarse”是否真的是当前 scaffold 必需件。","summary":"已集成并校验 `lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，建议以 r266 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 prototype probe，裁决“low-rank trunk + PK tiny cleanup”能否在约 `0.11x` total cost 下比当前 shared+PK scaffold 更强地压低 exceed。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0277.json:26:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u7b26\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u8fd0\u884c\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u3002r274-r276 \u5df2\u7ecf\u5728 dual-shared scaffold \u4e0a\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u4e0d\u591f\u5f3a\u7684 objective \u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d r275 \u867d\u6709\u6b63\u5411 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff0c\u4f46\u4ecd\u672a\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent\uff0c\u800c r276 \u7684 adaptive \u53d8\u4f53\u53c8\u56de\u9000\uff1b\u6309\u89c4\u5219\u6b64\u65f6\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c\u4e00 scaffold \u4e0a\u505a split/active-path \u90bb\u57df\u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5806 dual-shared \u53d8\u4f53\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u66f4\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u5e94\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u65b9\u5411\u201cshared bottleneck + expert-specific head\u201d\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u4fdd\u7559\u5f53\u524d\u5df2\u9a8c\u8bc1\u6709\u6548\u7684 PK cleanup \u8bed\u4e49\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\u843d\u5728 `~0.08x`\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e `shared_lowrank_*` \u65e7\u5bb6\u65cf\u5728\u5f53\u524d 1024-expert recipe \u4e0b\u7684 `~0.19x` \u9ad8\u6210\u672c\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u4fa7\u53ea\u65b0\u589e\u6700\u5c0f family\uff0c\u5e76\u5b8c\u6210 whitelist\u3001factory dispatch\u3001override allowlist\u3001compatibility registry \u4e0e exact-string smoke\uff1b\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e tunable env key\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u9700\u8981\u6539 `config_resolution`\u3001`runner` \u6216 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f\u4f4e\u79e9 shared bottleneck \u53ef\u80fd\u8fc7\u5f31\uff0cshared coarse \u53ea\u662f\u5728 cost \u4e0a\u66f4\u5de6\u5374\u6362\u4e0d\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff1b\u4f46\u8fd9\u6b63\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u3001\u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u7684\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784 probe\u3002",
