research/history/round_summaries/round_0228.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `topk`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S(x)} \u03b1_i(x) b_i`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `S(x)` \u662f\u5355\u5e93 top-k \u652f\u6301\u96c6\uff0c`{b_i}` \u662f\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e2d\u7684\u539f\u5b50\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201c\u9009\u62e9 + \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u5c5e\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1aRound 226 \u7684 `jumprelu` \u4e0e Round 227 \u7684 `group_topk` \u5df2\u628a\u201c\u6539\u9608\u503c\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u201d\u548c\u201c\u6539\u5206\u7ec4\u7ade\u4e89\u201d\u4e24\u6761\u5355\u5e93 selector \u652f\u7ebf\u90fd\u88c1\u6210\u5f3a\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u4f46\u5f53\u524d anchor recipe \u4e0b\u8fd8\u7f3a\u5c11 plain single-library top-k \u7684\u76f4\u63a5 closure probe\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u88c1\u51b3\u201c\u53bb\u6389 router / expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3001\u56de\u5230\u6700\u7b80\u5355\u5355\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u7a00\u758f\u548c\u201d\u662f\u5426\u53cd\u800c\u80fd\u5728\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u4e0a\u6539\u5584 exceed \u4ea4\u6362\u7387\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=1048576\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=1212416\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.2890625\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0 r212 \u7684 objective=0.35553750753402713\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed_alpha_0.50 \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u22640.06647500753402712`\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u6781\u9ad8\uff0c\u4f46\u5728\u5f53\u524d remaining compatible families \u91cc\uff0c\u5b83\u4ecd\u6bd4 `0.40x+` \u7684\u672a\u6d4b\u91cd\u7ed3\u6784\u66f4\u63a5\u8fd1\u73b0\u5b9e objective \u7a97\u53e3\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u80fd\u5b8c\u6210 current-target \u5bf9 single-library selector \u7ebf\u7684\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u4e2a\u7ed3\u6784\u88c1\u51b3\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0228.json:37:      "\u5f53\u524d `0.13x~0.21x` \u7684 matched architecture probes \u4e5f\u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a`factorized_expert_topk`\u3001`factorized_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u90fd\u672a\u628a objective \u62c9\u56de r212 \u9644\u8fd1\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。最终重构公式可写为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `{u_i}` 是由共享低秩 basis 导出的静态 shared 向量库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧先通过轻量 shared bottleneck / router 得到 shared 分支系数与少量激活 expert，再在对应静态库上做有限加权和。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表/加权和 + routed expert 子库查表 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前 round 172 的主问题不是继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上补 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 插值，而是寻找一个新的 `<0.25x` 结构槽位来挑战现有 low-cost anchor。相对 r171 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“在相同轻 trunk + 轻 routed recipe 下，加回一个更便宜的 shared bottleneck 分支，是否比纯 `lowrank_expert_topk` 更值得”。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:35:      "r168-r171 已连续给出同一 low-cost 邻域内的局部负信号：继续沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 轴补点，信息增量已经较低。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:41:      "如果该点在约 `0.22x` 下把 FVU 压到接近或优于当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=80/96` anchors，则下一轮继续留在该 family，只改 `K`，定位它在 `<0.25x` 内的 deployment knee。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:87:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0120.json:7:  "family_name": "two_stage_residual_expert",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0120.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i + Σ_{e∈E(r_1)} Σ_{j∈S_e(r_1)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r_1 = x - Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i。第一段在静态 coarse library B={b_i} 上做有限加权和，第二段对残差 r_1 用轻量 router 选择静态 expert 子库 {C_e} 并做局部 sparse residual 修正；在线导出仍是“coarse 查表 + expert residual 查表 + 有限加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。`topk`/`expert_topk`/`shared_routed_expert_topk` 属于直接兼容，`lowrank_expert_topk`/`lowrank_expert_residual`/`two_stage_residual_expert` 属于扩展兼容，`batch_topk`/`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 继续明确排除。r119 证明在 `K=96` 下把 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 设成“少 coarse、强 residual”只得到 FVU 0.1281，明显弱于 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 0.1030；同时历史 r54 也给出一致信号：对 `two_stage_residual_expert`，过低的 coarse 预算会伤害质量。唯一主假设：以 r119 为 reference，只把 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从 0.25 调到 0.5，在保持 `K=96, NUM_EXPERTS=32, EF=1, adam, 8e-4` 不变时，恢复更平衡的 `stage1_k=48 / stage2_k=48` 分配，若当前瓶颈主要来自 coarse stage 欠拟合而非 residual stage 不足，则 FVU 应明显优于 r119 的 0.1281，并更公平地回答 `two_stage_residual_expert` 在当前 target 上到底是结构不成立，还是仅仅预算分配错了。该调整基本不改变 total_cost，仍处于约 0.60x 的中低成本带内并低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0120.json:20:    "summary": "以 r119 为 reference，保持 `two_stage_residual_expert`、`K=96`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32` 与训练配方不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5`，验证当前两段式结构的失败是否主要来自 coarse/residual 分配过偏向 residual。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0120.json:23:    "family_name": "two_stage_residual_expert",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0120.json:35:      "r119 在当前 target 上给出 `two_stage_residual_expert K=96 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的真实结果：FVU 0.128086，明显弱于 matched `lowrank_expert_residual K=96` 的 0.102984，但仍略优于旧 `lowrank_expert_topk K=96` 的 0.130519。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0120.json:36:      "代码确认 `two_stage_residual_expert` 的默认分配为 `stage1_k = k // 2`；在 `K=96` 时，`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 对应 `stage1_k=24, stage2_k=72`，而 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` 对应 `stage1_k=48, stage2_k=48`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0120.json:40:      "如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` 明显优于 r119，则下一轮应继续留在 `two_stage_residual_expert`，再只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.75` 或 `K`，定位该 family 的最佳 coarse/residual 分工区间。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0120.json:42:      "如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` 只小幅改善但仍维持在约 0.12-0.13，则 `two_stage_residual_expert` 仍可作为中成本历史参考，但不应进入兼容 frontier 主线；下一轮应换 family 或换到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低 encoder 成本轴。"
