research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:33564:research/history/logs/agent_round_0157.stdout.log:658:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库，C={c_m} 是静态 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + routed expert sublibrary lookup + residual lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 与 r156 已经把两条 0.28x 的 shared-lowrank 无 residual 变体几乎等价地证伪，说明仅靠 shared low-rank coarse 或 routed top-k 还不够；下一步最有信息量的动作不是继续在这两条线上局部扫参，而是直接检验“hetero MoE + residual cleanup”能否在当前更压缩的 K=96 recipe 下重新形成中低成本结构段。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual”在约 0.53x total_cost 下是否仍值得继续。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.53x 下接近或优于当前 `<0.5x` best FVU=0.0984，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，测试这条 hetero-MoE+residual 线能否继续向 0.5x 左移。","如果该点明显劣于 r152 且不优于该 family 的既有最好结果，则可更明确地下调 shared-lowrank hetero residual 在当前 target 的优先级，后续不要继续在该 family 上做局部扫参。","如果该点质量介于 r147 与 r152 之间但仍形成新的中成本解释性锚点，则记录为 shared-lowrank hetero residual 只适合作为 0.5x 附近质量对照，而不是低成本主线。"],"notes_to_memory":["r155 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` FVU=0.14630839228630066，r156 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert @ K=96` FVU=0.14623424410820007；两条 shared-lowrank 无 residual 低成本线在当前 target 上都明显落后于 0.28x-0.30x frontier。","当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可正常运行。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=1843200，deployment_accesses=393216，combined_accesses=2236416，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.53，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮允许把预算上移到略高于 0.5x 的质量锚点，因为当前低成本两条 shared-lowrank 探针已连续失败；当前更重要的是回答 residual cleanup 是否能挽回这条 hetero-MoE 结构线。"],"reference_round":152,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。我没有返回代码改动，因为该 family 已经落盘且本地 smoke 通过；本轮更重要的是利用当前 matched recipe 做一次干净的结构切换。之所以不继续沿 r155/r156 的 0.28x 线做 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO` 微调，是因为它们已经在当前 target 上给出几乎相同的失败结果；而 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 是当前 shared-lowrank 方向里唯一还有历史正信号、且仍符合 operator hint 的 hetero-MoE+residual 候选。主要风险是 K 从 112/128 压到 96 后，该 family 可能仍被 r152 直接压制；但即使失败，也能更干净地终止一条当前仍未完全回答的结构假设。","summary":"建议本轮以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`。这是一次针对 hetero-MoE+residual 的 matched architecture probe，用来判断 shared-lowrank 方向在加入 residual cleanup 后，是否还能形成一个值得保留的 0.5x 左右结构锚点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:33566:research/history/logs/agent_round_0041.stdout.log:264:- `total_cost = selection_cost + deployment_cost`
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:33567:research/history/logs/agent_round_0178.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是由共享低秩分支导出的静态 shared 向量库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧只做 shared bottleneck 打分、轻量 router 选择少量 experts，并在静态 shared/expert 子库上做有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表/加权和 + routed expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能保留为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。r176 已确认 routed-only `expert_topk` 在当前 `K=108, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的轻 active-path recipe 下明显弱于 low-cost anchors，r177 又确认 fully factorized hetero-MoE 更差；因此当前更高信息量的问题是：问题到底在于“缺 shared branch”，还是在于“hetero/shared 方向整体不值得继续”。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“shared bottleneck + expert-specific full heads”这条高优先级结构槽位是否能在近低成本带提供比 routed-only 与 fully-factorized 更有价值的证据。本地成本自检显示该候选在当前 1024x4096 proxy 下 selection_accesses=647168、deployment_accesses=442368、combined_accesses=1089536，对应 combined_ratio 约 `0.26x`，虽然略高于主战场上沿，但仍明确处于允许的 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内，也显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 在约 `0.26x` 下明显优于 r176 的 routed-only `expert_topk`，并接近或优于它自己历史上的低成本结果，则说明 shared branch 仍有结构价值；下一轮可保持该 family 不变，只改 `K=96` 或 `K=112`，确认它在低成本辅助带的 deployment knee。","如果该点仍明显弱于当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors，且也没有优于 r176/r177 的结构对照，则可更明确地下调当前 target 上 `shared bottleneck + expert-specific head` 这条 hetero-MoE 分支优先级，转向其他尚未充分证伪的 very-light residual / factorized 方向。"],"notes_to_memory":["`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 导出形式应继续按 `扩展兼容` 处理：静态 shared 低秩库加静态 routed expert 子库上的有限加权和。","最近三轮 low-cost architecture probes 已给出更清晰的结构归因：r176 说明去掉 shared branch 的 routed-only `expert_topk` 明显偏弱，r177 说明把 hetero shared+routed 两端都 factorize 会更差。","本轮是一个 architecture-level matched-cost probe，不是继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线内补 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 插值。","本地成本自检：在 r165 的 recipe 上切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 后，selection_accesses=647168、deployment_accesses=442368、combined_accesses=1089536，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 total_cost 约 `0.26x`，处于当前允许的辅助对照带。"],"reference_round":165,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然该点略高于 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近三轮已经连续排除了 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，当前最需要的是用一个仍在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内的高优先级结构槽位，把“shared bottleneck + expert-specific head”这条线做一次更干净的 matched validation。选择它而不是继续回到 `factorized_expert_topk` 或 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，是因为前者已有更强负信号，后者又属于当前已明确下调优先级的 two-stage/hetero residual 方向。主要风险是该 family 在 r172/r174 已有偏弱结果；但这次是以当前更相关的 r165 low-cost anchor recipe 做 fresh matched probe，结论会更直接。","summary":"以 r165 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，做一轮 `0.26x` 左右的辅助带 architecture probe。目标是直接回答：在当前 low-cost anchor recipe 下，把 shared 分支改成更轻的 low-rank bottleneck、同时保留 expert-specific full heads，是否比 routed-only 或 fully-factorized 方向更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
