f8\u5bf9 r263\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u628a `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u4ece 56 \u964d\u5230 40\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`K=32`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5f53\u524d PK \u4e3b\u7ebf\u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u80fd\u628a controller `total_cost_ratio` \u4ece 0.08x \u538b\u5230 0.07x\u3002\u6309\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\uff0c`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=40` \u65f6 selection_accesses=147456\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=311296\u3001exact total_cost_ratio=0.07421875\uff0ccontroller \u4e24\u4f4d\u5c0f\u6570\u53e3\u5f84\u4e0b\u8bb0\u4e3a 0.07x\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u9884\u7b97\u3002\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d controller frontier\uff0c\u53ea\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.20600582122802735`\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u540c\u65f6\u5237\u65b0 r263 \u7684 exact objective\uff0c\u5219\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.20381825`\u3002\u8fd9\u8bf4\u660e `56 -> 40` \u4e0d\u662f\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u7ec6\u626b\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u771f\u6b63\u80fd\u8ba9 leaderboard \u6210\u672c\u518d\u5de6\u79fb\u4e00\u6863\u3001\u540c\u65f6\u4ecd\u5bb9\u8bb8\u9002\u5ea6 exceed \u56de\u5f39\u7684\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf width-knee probe\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0191.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_two_stage_residual_expert",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0191.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式写成 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(r)} Σ_{j∈S_e(r)} γ_{e,j}(r) c_{e,j}`，其中 `r = x - Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i`；`{u_i}` 是 shared coarse 静态向量库，`{c_{e,j}}` 是 expert residual 静态子库。它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表+加权求和，再做 expert residual 查表+选择性补偿”流水线，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。唯一主假设：相对 r188 仅切换到该 architecture，在保持 `K=96` 的 small-K low-cost recipe 下，显式把 shared/coarse branch 与 expert residual cleanup 分工开来，会比当前 small-K anchors 更慢地随 K 下降而退化，并在约 `0.23x total_cost` 内把 FVU 压到比现有 `K=96` 非 shared-routed probe 更低、且更接近 `<0.25x` 主前沿。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0191.json:20:    "summary": "建议以 r188 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_two_stage_residual_expert`。这是一次落在 `<0.25x` 主战场内的 small-K matched architecture probe，用最低额外成本直接验证“shared coarse branch + expert residual cleanup”能否在 `K=96` 比现有 low-cost probes 更稳。",
