research/history/round_summaries/round_0225.json:35:      "\u5f53\u524d `0.19x~0.21x` matched architecture probes \u5df2\u57fa\u672c\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_lowrank_*` \u90fd\u672a\u628a objective \u62c9\u56de r212 \u9644\u8fd1\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0184.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `factorized_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}`，其中 `h(x)=ReLU(Bx)` 是共享低维投影，`E(h(x))` 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，`{b_{e,i}}` 是各 expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧可直接导出为“shared low-rank projection + 轻量 expert 路由 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”的 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。r183 的新 family `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 在约 `0.24x` 下仅做到 `FVU=0.1411`，说明“shared coarse trunk + routed residual cleanup”这条 two-stage 变体没有打败现有 low-cost anchor；因此下一步更高信息量的问题不是继续在 shared/coarse 线上补参数，而是转向当前高优先级但尚未在这条 exact low-cost recipe 上 fresh 验证的“expert 内部 low-rank / small head”槽位。相对 r176 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“把 routed-only expert 的 full-dim 局部 scorer 换成 shared bottleneck + expert-specific small head，能否在更低总成本下修复 r176 的质量缺口”。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0184.json:38:      "r183 的 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 已在约 `0.24x` 失败并归档，当前不应继续沿 shared-coarse two-stage 线做局部参数补点。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0261.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e^\u03c4(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\u3002\u5176\u4e2d {b_{e,i}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff0cE_pk(x) \u7531\u4e24\u8def product-key router \u7ed9\u51fa\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0cS_e^\u03c4(x) \u7531 expert \u5185 JumpReLU \u5f62\u6210\u5c40\u90e8\u7a00\u758f\u652f\u6301\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cleft/right product-key \u6253\u5206 -> \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u50cf `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u8fd9\u7c7b\u5e26 shared/trunk \u7684\u5bb6\u65cf\u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk`\u3001`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` \u8fd9\u7c7b sample/batch-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e8e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u771f\u5b9e compatible incumbent \u4e0d\u662f\u63d0\u793a\u91cc\u7684\u65e7 `expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u800c\u662f r251 `product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u5176 controller frontier objective\u22480.293524=0.10x+0.193524\uff0cexact round-summary objective=0.290692=0.097168x+0.193524\uff0c\u4e14\u8bad\u7ec3\u66f2\u7ebf `curve_still_improving=true`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u4ecd\u6709\u9ad8\u4ef7\u503c\u672a\u9a8c\u8bc1\u5047\u8bbe\uff0c\u4e0d\u5c5e\u4e8e\u5e94\u7acb\u5373\u5207\u69fd\u7684\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u5c40\u90e8\u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u76f8\u5bf9 r251 \u53ea\u628a `NUM_EXPERTS` \u4ece 512 \u63d0\u5230 1024\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`K=32`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=96`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5173\u952e\u7684 mainline \u5bb9\u91cf\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u5df2\u627e\u5230\u7684\u7a84 micro-expert knee \u4e0a\uff0c\u66f4\u5927\u7684 compositional bank \u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u80fd\u4ee5\u51e0\u4e4e\u4e0d\u53d8\u7684 rounded cost \u6362\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u591a\u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\u3002\u6309\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\uff0c`NUM_EXPERTS=1024` \u65f6 `left_keys=32,right_keys=32`\uff0cselection_accesses=262144\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=425984\u3001exact total_cost_ratio=0.1015625\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u9884\u7b97\uff1bcontroller \u4e24\u4f4d\u5c0f\u6570\u53e3\u5f84\u4e0b\u4ecd\u8bb0\u4e3a 0.10x\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0 controller frontier \u53ea\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1935243308544159`\uff0c\u800c\u82e5\u8981\u540c\u65f6\u5237\u65b0 r251 \u7684 exact objective\uff0c\u5219\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1891295`\u3002r252 \u5df2\u7ecf\u8bc1\u660e\u5728\u540c\u6837 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=96` \u4e0b\u628a bank \u964d\u5230 256 \u4f1a\u8ba9 exceed \u6076\u5316\u5230 0.209794\uff1b\u4e0e\u6b64\u540c\u65f6\uff0cr248 \u4e5f\u8bc1\u660e\u5728\u66f4\u5bbd `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` \u4e0b\u628a bank \u63d0\u5230 1024 \u7684\u786e\u80fd\u6362\u56de\u66f4\u4f4e exceed\u3002\u56e0\u6b64 `1024 @ width=96` \u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u9644\u8fd1\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u6700\u5927\u3001\u4e14\u5c1a\u672a\u5728\u5f53\u524d knee \u4e0a\u88ab\u9a8c\u8bc1\u7684\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u5bb9\u91cf probe\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 coarse bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是 shared/coarse 分支的静态向量库，`r(x)=x-x_coarse` 表示经第一阶段 shared/coarse 重构后的残差，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert residual 子库的静态原子；在线侧先用极便宜的 shared low-rank/coarse 分支吃掉平滑主干，再让少量 routed experts 只做静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared/coarse 查表 + routed residual expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前额外提示已把问题收束到“保持 very short active path，同时增大总容量，并让 shared/coarse branch 负责主干、routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”；在已知 `expert_topk` 与 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 都给出新的低成本负信号后，当前最有信息量的下一问不是继续在同一 family 补 `K/LATENTS`，而是用一个真正改变‘容量与激活路径关系’的结构槽位做 matched architecture probe。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“cheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup”是否比近期失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 方向更接近当前 low-cost anchors。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:20:    "summary": "以 r165 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，做一轮约 `0.26x` 的辅助带 architecture probe。目标是直接回答：把 cheap shared/coarse branch 明确改成主干表示、只让 routed experts 做 sparse residual cleanup，是否比最近失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 低成本方向更接近当前 anchors。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:23:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然当前阶段强调 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近两轮已经连续否定 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，用一个仍留在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内、且真正改变“shared 主干 vs residual cleanup”分工关系的结构槽位做 probe，信息增量高于继续在线性 `K/LATENTS` 轴上补点。选择 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 而不是 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，是因为它更贴合本轮新增提示里“先用极便宜 shared/coarse branch 吃掉平滑主干，再让 routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”的结构假设。主要风险是该 family 属于已被部分下调优先级的 shared-lowrank/two-stage 类别；但它是当前仍处在低成本辅助带、且与最新策略提示最匹配的现成结构。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:30:        "value": "shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:35:      "`shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 的 LUTurbo 导出形式应按 `扩展兼容` 处理：静态 shared/coarse 库加静态 routed residual expert 子库上的有限加权和。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:42:      "如果 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 在约 `0.26x` 下把 FVU 压到接近或优于其历史 `K=112` 结果，并明显优于最近的 routed-only / fully-factorized probes，则下一轮可保持该 family 不变，只改 `K=96` 或 `K=112`，确认它在低成本辅助带的 deployment knee。",
